rows.label: qst400909_msg0002
rows.name:
So it looks like they're being taken to
a facility around the Superbia Divine Beast's
chest area, huh...?

rows.label: qst400909_msg0003
rows.name:
Indeed. Apparently a number of
Nopon came and carried the barrels
off in that direction.

rows.label: qst400909_msg0004
rows.name:
Perhaps it is time we reported our
findings to the Flamebringer.

rows.label: qst400909_msg0006
rows.name:
If we visit the palace, the guards
should take us to her, as I recall?

rows.label: qst400909_msg0008
rows.name:
Here's hoping we don't get surrounded
and attacked again, instead.
